bug.short_desc: [epub] Automatic inclusion of referenced resources fail on anchor references

long_desc.thetext:
When using the Ant task "includeReferenced" option in order to automatically pick up and include referenced files it will fail when parsing a link that contains an anchor reference.
/Users/torkild/git/epub-examples/book/build.xml:73: java.lang.IllegalArgumentException: "file" /Users/torkild/git/org.eclipse.mylyn.docs/org.eclipse.mylyn.docs.epub.help/docs/epub-ant-task.html#Publicationtitle must exist.
One can get around this issue by using **fileset** sub-elements to include files.
Created attachment 213741 Patch to handle anchor references
